  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Kdepimlibs</title>

    <para>Installez <application>kdepimlibs</application> en lançant les commandes
    suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

<!-- Again, nothing in sysconfdir -->
<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd build &amp;&amp;
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=&kde-dir; -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

